{"tid":1628271,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【人權民主法案】","createTime":"2019-10-06T01:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:40:00.000Z","uid":44358,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd426d51e31b24f8477ffd40747e150c1360b6e","tid":1628271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:59:03.000Z","msg":"今個月美國就快通過人權民主法案。<br />\n<br />\n上個月你問我，我覺得通過機會九成九。到今日，我估大家冇肯定答案。如果以美國利益嚟講，其實通過機會重係樂觀。但有啲可能會修改，尤其係保障示威者方面。<br />\n<br />\n大家知道法案會保障大部份示威者，不會被美國拒絕申請ＶＩＳＡ權利，令義士有機會進行第二人生。但問題再攪裝修，觀感上令美國對大家有介心，隨時會改法案內容。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國會，其實都有中蟈滲透，佢地平時未必敢反對法案，但當見有機會，美國人唔支持大家，佢地就會振振有詞反對法案。"},{"pid":"0260f2dc15bc3a2d8ca5339db0faf2092f934e28","tid":1628271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:05:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec3a9828b997044d3cfa775b7ef5da81f610498","tid":1628271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0ce8489ae2229c11cf1f6c2f5ed303acdfb76e","tid":1628271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522ef5469357d9fd5734e7473a4b8e4777d0ffdf","tid":1628271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif